143.7161, 142.733, 143.731, 143.1226, 141.9756, 141.3923, 141.0801, 140.9273, 139.2274, 140.2546, 140.1213, 139.4812, 139.8247, 140.0742, 140.5407, 140.7498, 139.0567, 139.0145, 139.089, 138.5548, 138.7406, 137.4792, 137.4585, 138.0455, 136.6823, 138.0828, 138.2513, 138.3889, 137.5389, 137.9554, 138.0094, 137.4171, 137.5469, 136.9531, 136.4307, 136.1784, 136.9409, 138.6421, 139.0989, 138.6728, 138.6948, 139.4007, 139.2765, 138.7402, 140.1477, 140.2492, 140.4003, 139.3485, 138.5045, 139.6765, 139.408, 139.4652, 140.8042, 140.5004, 140.8747, 139.4773, 138.622, 137.8067, 136.8896, 136.445, 135.745, 136.0216, 134.6771, 133.6928, 133.4922, 133.4321, 132.2473, 135.1444, 134.3761, 133.9952, 134.1534, 133.1047, 133.4021, 133.8116, 132.887, 132.3767, 132.8076, 133.7866, 132.8592, 133.7078, 133.8528, 134.016, 135.2603, 134.7061, 135.8156, 136.9396, 137.4252, 137.2092, 137.3211, 136.9207, 136.2703, 136.696, 137.5697, 136.9523, 136.8246, 136.2092, 135.0421, 135.9417, 137.486, 135.7536, 135.3931, 134.8944, 134.1016, 133.8138, 133.8797, 134.4975, 133.092, 131.1239, 132.0639, 132.9516, 133.4016, 134.8437, 134.2988, 133.1129, 133.3325, 130.631, 128.7791, 127.7693, 128.7922, 128.8568, 127.6593, 126.5283, 127.6263, 127.9949, 129.6535, 129.7486, 129.6076, 129.3601, 129.123, 128.2962, 129.7453, 129.7047, 129.6441, 127.8476, 128.7473, 128.2797, 129.6097, 130.6704, 130.0113, 130.122, 130.3165, 130.138, 129.7272, 130.326, 129.8663, 130.4476, 130.865, 130.7839, 129.188, 128.6685, 128.5668, 128.9102, 128.9326, 129.6134, 129.4703, 129.9085, 129.621, 129.5847, 130.3556, 131.1269, 131.8309, 131.6701, 129.411, 129.4188, 128.678, 129.9247, 130.8733, 130.6608, 132.2033, 133.1003, 133.8301, 134.7116, 134.5717, 134.2814, 135.201, 134.2098, 133.2399, 133.2167, 133.5551, 131.4557, 131.3084, 129.4142, 128.7866, 129.5479, 130.4005, 130.2126, 129.1971, 129.6216, 129.2228, 130.704, 130.8231, 131.5341, 132.916, 131.5564, 130.0759, 131.1338, 130.5786, 131.9342, 133.0349, 133.7211, 134.7625, 135.8881, 136.8917, 136.9742, 137.5662, 139.1057, 139.8498, 140.358, 137.7472, 135.4585, 136.9816, 136.7224, 137.0609, 137.1619, 137.6814, 140.1483, 139.5193, 139.9856, 140.7637, 139.3325, 139.299, 140.6014, 142.0454, 140.8622, 139.7602], "summary_html": "<h1>cb_ls_H15_Q15 — Carry+Basis 复合多空因子</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报构建了需求、供给、库存、价差、利润五大类基本面因子，以滚动胜率加权合成信号对玻璃期货做多空择时。复现时将因子逻辑泛化到全品种商品期货：利用数据中可得的展期收益（<code>ryminusema252</code>）和基差（<code>basis</code>）作为 carry/价差因子的截面排名信号，两者等权组合后做多低排名（backwardation + 高基差）品种、做空高排名（contango + 低基差）品种。这一策略能赚钱的核心逻辑是：期限结构和基差反映了商品供需紧缺程度，backwardation（近月升水）通常对应库存紧张/现货强势，买入这些品种可获取展期收益和价格上涨的双重回报。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.89</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>5.5%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>6.2%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-9.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.05</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>2969</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.07</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.69</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.25 / 0.9</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>1.44</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.12</span></td><td>0.34</td><td>0.74</td><td>1.57</td><td>1.14</td><td>1.89</td><td>0.75</td><td>1.45</td><td>1.01</td><td>0.7</td><td>0.2</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">3.26</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>ryminusema252</code></td><td>展期收益EMA</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>basis</code></td><td>基差</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 15 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 15 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>49</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>2971</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>30.4%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>12.1</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rank}_{i,t}^{\\text{ryema}} = \\text{CrossSectionalRank}\\left(\\text{ryminusema252}_{i,t}\\right) \\in [0, 1]</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{rank}_{i,t}^{\\text{basis}} = \\text{CrossSectionalRank}\\left(\\text{basis}_{i,t}\\right) \\in [0, 1]</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{combo}_{i,t} = \\frac{\\text{rank}_{i,t}^{\\text{ryema}} + \\text{rank}_{i,t}^{\\text{basis}}}{2}</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_{i,t} = \\begin{cases} +1 &amp; \\text{if } \\text{ComboRank}_{i,t} \\geq 1 - q \\\\ -1 &amp; \\text{if } \\text{ComboRank}_{i,t} \\leq q \\\\ 0 &amp; \\text{otherwise} \\end{cases}, \\quad q = 0.15</div>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{position}_{i,t} = \\text{signal}_{i,t} \\times \\frac{\\sigma_{\\text{target}}}{\\hat{\\sigma}_{i,t}}, \\quad \\text{clipped to } [-2, 2]</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{ryminusema252}</span> 为展期收益的 EMA(252) 累加值，<span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{basis}</span> 为期现基差，<span class=\"math-tex\">q</span> 为多空分位阈值，<span class=\"math-tex\">\\sigma_{\\text{target}} = 0.15</span>。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>5大类基本面因子全部实现（库存/基差/利润/持仓/仓单），最优为ry_ema (0.88)。库存(-0.36)和利润(-0.64)因子方向错误，拖累组合。</td><td>基线建立：17个变体覆盖5因子 + 3种组合</td><td>Sharpe 0.88，通过backtest gate</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>Carry/Basis因子主导(0.80-0.88)，库存/利润/持仓因子均弱。利润两个方向都为负。组合被弱因子稀释。</td><td>剪枝弱因子，只保留carry+basis；加hold grid(5/10/15)和IC gate；尝试翻转利润方向确认无效</td><td><strong>关键转折</strong>: Sharpe 0.88→1.17。carry+basis 2因子combo(cb_ls_H5)为最优。TS IC从-0.003翻正到0.009。</td></tr><tr><td>R3</td><td>最优在H5 hold=5天，换手率1.03偏高；需参数精细化。</td><td>加long_q grid(0.15/0.20/0.30) + vol_target grid(0.10/0.15/0.20)；H延长至15天降换手</td><td>Sharpe 1.17→1.31。Q15+H15为最优，换手率降至0.49，MaxDD从-29%改善到-21%。</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频（<code>comm_data/daily/kline_daynight_all.parquet</code>）</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（约49个有carry/basis数据的品种）</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 15日再平衡，中长期持有</li>\n<li><strong>核心依赖</strong>: <code>ryminusema252</code> (展期收益EMA) 和 <code>basis</code> (期现基差) 两个基本面字段</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 研报原始5因子中仅carry+basis在全品种有效，库存/利润/持仓信号在跨品种截面上无效\n<p>- 与因子库已有carry因子(zhongxin_combo)相关性0.68，存在冗余风险 - 前半段Sharpe(2.02)显著高于后半段(0.84)，近年信号衰减 - 非空率约28-37%，部分品种/时段缺失carry/basis数据</p>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.16s</li>\n</ul>"}